<para>Width in pixels of the stroke. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>If stroke width of zero is passed, it will be ignored and will not change the value stored in GContext. Currently, only odd stroke_width values are supported. If an even value is passed in, the value will be stored as is, but the drawing routines will round down to the previous integral value when drawing. Default value is 1. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
